{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take photos and document the world's most elusive legends, including Bigfoot, Dracula and the Loch Ness Monster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After a once-in-a-lifetime encounter with Bigfoot, you find yourself drawn into a deeper mystery. Chasing a lead to the Bermuda Triangle, you run aground on an uncharted island - a refuge for mythical and legendary creatures. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore Enchanting Biomes</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/explorecropped.gif?t=1739411524\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Journey through vibrant and magical landscapes, each with its own surprises. From rugged coastlines to snowy mountain peaks, and from castle-dotted lochs to mysterious forests\u2014new creatures and secrets await you at every turn.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Capture the Perfect Photo</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/nessycropped.gif?t=1739411524\" />Every photo is graded on its quality, with top-tier shots earning more and unlocking new content. Capture creatures in rare moments and unique poses for even greater value! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Complete Your Creature Compendium</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/compendiumcropped.gif?t=1739411524\" />Fill your compendium with your most prized Polaroids, documenting each legendary creature you discover.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unlock New Gadgets</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/gadgets-cropped.gif?t=1739411524\" />Gain access to tools that interact with the world around you. These gadgets help you uncover hidden paths, provoke rare behaviors in creatures, and enhance your exploration. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unravel the Mystery of the Bermuda Triangle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Why do vehicles vanish in the Bermuda Triangle? Why have the world\u2019s most elusive creatures found refuge there? As a daring explorer and photographer, it\u2019s up to you to solve this age-old mystery. </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739411524","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/page.bg.jpg?t=1739411524","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/ad80444573582bfefcc0e18f4829e859b17663a0/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739411524","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/ad80444573582bfefcc0e18f4829e859b17663a0/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739411524","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Tracked Controller Support","id":52},{"description":"VR Only","id":54},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take photos and document the world's most elusive legends, including Bigfoot, Dracula and the Loch Ness Monster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After a once-in-a-lifetime encounter with Bigfoot, you find yourself drawn into a deeper mystery. Chasing a lead to the Bermuda Triangle, you run aground on an uncharted island - a refuge for mythical and legendary creatures. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore Enchanting Biomes</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/explorecropped.gif?t=1739411524\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Journey through vibrant and magical landscapes, each wit